Arame CRM Privacy Policy
This privacy policy explains how personal data will be used by Arame CRM in relation to the use of the app that link to this policy.
We are sharing this information to explain how your ‘personal data’ and 'personally identifiable information' - that can be used on its own or with other data/information to identify, contact, or locate a person - is being used in connection with our services. Please read this policy carefully to get a clear understanding of how we collect and use your ‘personal data’ and 'personally identifiable information'.
Who are we?
Aramesul is a factory located in São José dos Pinhais, Brazil, referred to as "Arame CRM", "we", "us" or "our" in this policy.
You can contact us at: 1136 Saracura Street, Campo Largo da Roseira, São José dos Pinhais – PR, Brazil. 
You may also email us at ti.arametrix@outlook.com.
When do we collect information?
We collect your information directly when you provide information e.g. by registering to use Arame CRM or contact us (online or offline).
What personal data do we collect from the people that use our app?
When using our app, you may be asked to enter your name, email address. 
We will process your login details: including username and password and similar credentials.
What is the purpose for collecting the information?
Ultimately, we collect information because this app is made to Aramesul sellers only and to protect and ensure safety of our services and products and our confidential and proprietary information.
How long will we use your personal data
We shall be storing your information as long as you use the app.
Contacting Us
If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy, you may contact us at ti.arametrix@outlook.com.
Cookie Policy
Do we use 'cookies'?
No.
